<span id="freeTextContainer9213259080855420983">Morrison is my master distiller - all essence, no excess. And I can&apos;t recall another book with such an organically perfect, mike-dropping ending. Morrison&apos;s writing is so smooth that this short book reads very quickly; I know I burned through it too fast and will need to reread several more times, maybe with the idea of mercy in the forefront of my mind. There are so many ways to read this book!</span>
  <span id="freeText9213259080855420983" style="display:none">Morrison is my master distiller - all essence, no excess. And I can't recall another book with such an organically perfect, mike-dropping ending. Morrison's writing is so smooth that this short book reads very quickly; I know I burned through it too fast and will need to reread several more times, maybe with the idea of mercy in the forefront of my mind. There are so many ways to read this book!</span>
