<li class='cover' id='bookCover_51541232'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/51541232-telephone"><img alt="Telephone" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1573000040l/51541232._SX98_SY160_.jpg" />
